{%- comment -%}
  preload-assets — preload tags for LCP image + critical fonts.

  Phase 1: no preload needed. Hero is inline SVG <symbol id="bottle">,
  renders with first byte of HTML; no separate image fetch.
  No web fonts (system stack).

  Phase 2: if merchant uploads a hero image via dim-hero settings, this
  snippet will emit:
    <link rel="preload" as="image" href="{HERO_IMAGE}" fetchpriority="high">
{%- endcomment -%}
